  m_text: "Aether Terra is a world made up of six floating islands suspended over
    a vast sky. This world has diverse ecosystems, cultures, and environments among
    its islands.\n\nA perfect mirror of this world\u2013 umbra terra is where your
    journey takes place. The price of magic is high, so its side effects reside in
    this world. After centuries upon centuries of peace, Umbra Terra has begun to
    overflow, its negative magic leaking through the world\u2019s seams as fractures
    which must be sealed by a powerful hero\u2013 you.\n\nAs the last descendent
    of the mages responsible for Umbra Terra, it is your responsibility to venture
    into this vast world. Using the power of mysterious gem shards, you must seal
    all the fractures, and save your two worlds from merging into one. "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
